data.description: Are you seeking a centrally located home with nearly all newer mechanicals (2022), a privacy fenced-in backyard, and a partially finished full basement? Located on a dead end street just minutes from shopping, this 4BR/1BA home features a covered entrance, a 0.24acre lot, and a two-car garage. Complete with a spacious living room, an eat-in kitchen, two bedrooms on the main level, a full bathroom with a shower/tub combo and two additional bedrooms upstairs. Perfect for entertaining, the full basement includes a bar and a family room. Updates in 2022 include; a new roof, new gutters and downspouts, new A/C, new furnace, new water lines, new electric panel and new vinyl floors. All you need to do is bring your unique style and personal touches to create your dream home!
